Practical version (so it actually pays off)

* Invest attention → things that compound
    (skills, relationships, building)
* Limit leakage → things that drain without return
    (doomscrolling, noise, over-analysis loops)
* Reframe signals → like you said earlier
    (anxiety → readiness, pressure → opportunity)

